# AWS S3 Static Website Hosting Automation using Python (boto3)

## Project Overview

This project automates the deployment of a static website on Amazon S3 using Python and the boto3 SDK.

The automation script performs the following tasks:

* Creates an Amazon S3 bucket
* Enables Static Website Hosting
* Configures bucket policies for public access
* Uploads website files automatically
* Hosts the website using the S3 website endpoint

---

## Architecture

```text
Python Script (boto3)
        │
        ▼
   Amazon S3 Bucket
        │
        ▼
 Upload HTML/CSS/JS Files
        │
        ▼
 Enable Static Website Hosting
        │
        ▼
 Public Website Endpoint
```

---

## AWS Services Used

* Amazon S3
* AWS IAM
* Python boto3 SDK

